relation: Oh. My. God. Jabba is dancing. Right, now wheres my gun...
AXE. For your dirty Bounty Hunters.
Yeah, I do my own stunts. Don't look so surprised.
I told you ladies already, I can't kill your husbands and run away with you. At least... not for free.
How much for Cyndi Lauper and Yoko Ono?
Boba, is that a blaster in your pocket or are you just happy to see us?
Opening tonight for the Max Rebo Band at Jabba's Palace, Boba and the Slave 1's. They'll be performing their number one hit, "He's No Good To Me Dead."
Put them both in the cargo hold.
There, I dyed her hair red and added two pointy things on the sides of her head. Now pay up, Jabba.
Sorry ladie, but I busy right now. Maybe after I kill Han.
Hey Boba! Did you eat all the spagetti? Cause if you did, I'll blast your head off along with JarJar binks!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
I wonder if nows the perfect time to push her into the Rancor cage....
Jabba, i thought i was going to be paid in credits...
Sorry Miss, but I don't date girls who are taller than me
*pet pet pet* "You have such lovely fuzzy hair, Rystal...now about Jodo Kast..."
Hey, look at me, hey. Look at me I comannd that you look at me! Awwww why aren't you looking at me!?
That's right carrot top, I got your sister and there is nothing you can do about it!

When I am out hunting down Jedi and Rebel scum, I get really thristy, so I stop off a Jabba's Pleaseure Palace for the usual, Beer, women and watching the Rancor rip apart some rebel scum. So come on down and join me at Jabba's!
Being a bounty hunter never lets you do the things you want.

How you doin'? I'm doing goo.....wait I'm talking to myself again, the girls aren't even looking at me. Jabba's gonna throw me into the Sarlacc Pit if I don't stop! I gotta lean against this wall so I can get my head straight.
It's good to be the Fett
Um... +clears throat+ Ladies... ladies! I'm over here! Not there! Here! Right here!
Ok ok, I'll play the bounty hunter and you can be.......... wierd fish girl?
Boba Fett loved taking over the pimp's jobs when he was fed to the Rancor...
Ahh... the woman love a guy in battle armor... maybe its just they don't want me to shoot them.

At the moment Boba Fett is happy, however he wont be when he sees out of the sides of his narrow helmet that one of the girls standing next to him has two tails sticking out of her head, and the other is purple.
OK Rystall,......time to die! MUAHAHAHAHAHAHHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHHAAH! heehee.
Okay, I walk over to her, tap her chin.... oh for Pete's sake! Who writes this crap? *goes over and shoots Rystall*
No girls, I didn't kill George Lucas back in 1983, but I should have!!
Boba... the greatest bounty hunter in the galaxy... Rystall... the greatest tease in the galaxy...
I'll have what Boba is having....
Are you ladies together? Or do I have to buy you separately?
Do yor perfer a man in or out of uniform?
To be or not to be. That is the question.
Hey Jabba, these girls are telling me there's a tapioca tea named after me. When did this happen?
...And so Boba Fett began taking dance classes to broaden his horizons... by putting broads in his horizon...
Alright you two! break it up! There will not be no fighting or hair pulling in this palace!

where is a bouty when you need one because bount hunters can get real bored after you have been waiting for a pretty long time,ooooohhhhhhh what do we have here(nobody has givin me boutys so mabee...)it is my day off! Time to go on a date.

With a rash like that maybe I should leave the armor on...
WHAT THE HECK AM I DOING?
Dad made me through cloning, now I see why! Nothing but twi-leks and...what the hell are you!?
Meet Bob...er...Boba, he was just like you, until he made a call to enzyte, now look at him!
Unfortunately, at that point, Boba Fett's alarm clock went off, and he had to spend another pointless day looking for Darth Vader's television remote.

Excuse me ladies, but I have to go try and kill the galaxy's last hope and later be knocked into one of the galaxy's most dangerous predator by a blind man swinging a stick.
